1102
01:40:39,351 --> 01:40:41,251
What do you mean,
she's gone?

1103
01:41:03,575 --> 01:41:04,507
Hey!

1104
01:41:06,244 --> 01:41:07,438
Wait!

1105
01:41:28,500 --> 01:41:30,695
