I'm not going to hurt you.

1106
01:41:32,170 --> 01:41:33,569
Trust me!

1107
01:41:47,085 --> 01:41:48,712
(gasp)

1108
01:41:56,361 --> 01:41:57,885
You know...

1109
01:41:59,764 --> 01:42:01,356
I thought that...

1110
01:42:02,367 --> 01:42:04,801
if I'd leave her alone...

1111
01:42:06,071 --> 01:42:08,198
she'd stop
being afraid of me.

1112
01:42:12,177 --> 01:42:13,508
I just...

1113
01:42:15,647 --> 01:42:17,979
I just left her there.

1114
01:42:27,158 --> 01:42:29,592
When I got home,
I saw her...

1115
01:42:32,030 --> 01:42:34,590
I saw her shoe

1116
01:42:34,666 --> 01:42:37,533
on the floor of my car.

1117
01:42:42,641 --> 01:42:44,233
And l...

1118
01:42:48,446 --> 01:42:51,745
Jesus, I just wanted
to help the woman...

1119
01:42:55,487 --> 01:42:57,421
Why didn't you report it, Nik?

1120
01:42:59,124 --> 01:43:02,252
Because I thought
she'd be all right.

1121
01:43:03,328 --> 01:43:05,728
I thought she'd find
her way out of there.

1122
01:43:10,869 --> 01:43:12,427
Then when l...

1123
01:43:14,706 --> 01:43:16,833
and when
I saw her on the news...

1124
01:43:17,976 --> 01:43:20,672
that she was missing, l...

1125
01:43:28,386 --> 01:43:31,844
By then who was going
to believe me?

1126
01:43:44,903 --> 01:43:46,495
Thank you...

1127
01:43:47,572 --> 01:43:49,335
for letting me know.

1128
01:43:50,909 --> 01:43:52,376
Bye.

1129
01:44:19,104 --> 01:44:21,572
Paula? Come in.

1130
01:44:21,640 --> 01:44:23,369
Hi.

1131
01:44:28,713 --> 01:44:30,772
Hey, sweetie.

1132
01:44:34,285 --> 01:44:37,686
- Paula: Daddy will be home soon.
- Maybe they can come back later.

1133
01:44:37,756 --> 01:44:41,556
- They've been so good for me.
- No, I don't think so.

1134
01:44:43,561 --> 01:44:44,858
Paula.

1135
01:44:46,031 --> 01:44:47,999
He didn't do it, Jane.

1136
01:44:50,802 --> 01:44:52,497
How do you know?

1137
01:44:55,974 --> 01:44:57,532
He told me.

1138
01:45:05,216 --> 01:45:06,444
Paula?

1139
01:45:07,886 --> 01:45:09,820
Jane:
What could I do, Paula?

1140
01:45:11,589 --> 01:45:12,749
All right.

1141
01:45:12,824 --> 01:45:16,123
Go inside and put
your bags in your rooms.

1142
01:45:31,342 --> 01:45:33,003
Stupid...

1143
01:45:35,547 --> 01:45:38,038
You've got no right, Jane!

1144
01:45:38,116 --> 01:45:40,050
