1146
01:45:42,120 --> 01:45:45,419
I don't want to see you
anywhere near my kids again.

1147
01:47:39,671 --> 01:47:42,367
I was home, Leon.

1148
01:47:47,779 --> 01:47:50,145
I didn't pick up the phone.

1149
01:47:54,252 --> 01:47:56,686
Valerie on tape:
John? There's a man...

1150
01:47:56,754 --> 01:47:58,517
Patrick.

1151
01:47:58,590 --> 01:48:00,683
He's a client and he's...

1152
01:48:00,758 --> 01:48:02,589
