to be happening to us.

1157
01:48:17,909 --> 01:48:20,878
Oh... there are lights.

1158
01:48:20,945 --> 01:48:23,607
There's a car coming.
I'll wave it down.

1159
01:48:25,250 --> 01:48:28,708
Wait for me.
We'll talk when I get home, okay?

1160
01:48:28,786 --> 01:48:30,481
Bye.

1161
01:48:30,555 --> 01:48:32,785
I love you.

1162
01:48:34,826 --> 01:48:36,259
(machine beeps)

1163
01:48:39,864 --> 01:48:42,992
I thought she would come home.

1164
01:49:40,325 --> 01:49:43,726
Sonja, on tape:
It's not that he might have...

1165
01:49:43,795 --> 01:49:46,389
