1169
01:50:02,146 --> 01:50:04,273
Valerie:
Do you still love him?

1170
01:50:12,890 --> 01:50:15,188
Sonja: Yeah.

1171
01:50:15,259 --> 01:50:17,022
I still love him.

1172
01:52:05,636 --> 01:52:08,161
I don't want to lose you.

1173
01:52:10,274 --> 01:52:12,299
